timing_driving...erride_library(25.10)  timing_driving...erride_library(25.10)

Name
       timing_driving_cell_override_library

Syntax
       timing_driving_cell_override_library

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Controls  the  selection  of library cells specified using the set_dri-
       ving_cell command.

       When set to true, a driving cell will be picked up from the Max Library
       for max drive cell adjustment and Min Library for min  drive  cell  ad-
       justment,  irrespective  of  the  library  specified  with the set_dri-
       ving_cell -library parameter.

       When set to false, the libraries are selected  as  specified  with  the
       set_driving_cell command.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

